# Webview UI

## Stack

- React + Vite in `webview-ui/` (separate from esbuild host bundle).
- Acquire VS Code API once: `const vscode = acquireVsCodeApi()`.

## Accessibility (R-PLAT-9)

- Tab order for all interactive controls; visible focus rings.
- `aria-live="polite"` for streaming completion announcements.
- Non-empty `aria-label` on icon-only buttons.

## Panels

- Conversation Pane: Design stage only; read-only banner in Build/Deploy.
- Tab Workspace tabs (fixed order): Task, Architecture, Requirement, Commit, Deploy.

## State

- Persist layout split ratio and last tab per workspace via host messages.
- Never store secrets in webview `localStorage`.
